<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4535038>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 21. — A, Megacanthopora enodata n. sp., longitudinal section showing autozooecial walls with aktinotostyles and mural spines, paratype SMF 21.895. B-D, Rectifenestella sp., SMF 21.898, tangential section; E-I, Spinofenestella major (Nikiforova, 1933) comb. nov., SMF 21.899; E-G, tangential section of the colony; H, mid-tangential section of the branch showing autozooecial chambers with hemisepta; I, tangential section of the branch showing autozooecial apertures. Scale bars: A, C, G, 1 mm; B, E, 2 mm, D, H, I, 0.2 mm; F, 0.5 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4535038/files/figure.png" .

